rowers%20who%20miss%20payments%20could%20suffer%20hits%20to%20their%20credit%20scores%2C%20and%20defaulted%20payments%20could%20prompt%20wage%20garnishment%20and%20the%20seizure%20of%20federal%20benefits%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-will-social-security-benefits-run-out-retirement-crisis-boomers-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESocial%20Security%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20advocates%20have%20called%20on%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20extend%20the%20on-ramp%20period%20given%20other%20financial%20challenges%20facing%20millions%20of%20borrowers%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20preventing%20many%20of%20them%20from%20getting%20lower%20monthly%20payments%20through%20the%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%20%E2%80%94%20a%20left-leaning%20think%20tank%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanprogress.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2024%2F09%2FLetter-to-ED_Extending-On-Ramp-for-Repayment36.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20on%20September%2018%20urging%20him%20to%20extend%20the%20on-ramp%20period%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20student%20loan%20system%20is%20hashed%20out%20in%20court%2C%20borrowers%20need%20continued%20support%20in%20the%20form%20of%20an%20extended%20on-ramp.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBetween%20ongoing%20servicer%20issues%2C%20the%20legal%20injunction%20preventing%20the%20Department%20from%20implementing%20portions%20of%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20and%20other%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%2C%20and%20the%20associated%20confusion%20around%20administrative%20forbearance%2C%20borrowers%20need%20more%20time%20to%20successfully%20navigate%20their%20student%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20previously%20said%20that%20it%20did%20not%20have%20any%20plans%20to%20extend%20the%20on-ramp%20period%2C%20and%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20the%20department%20will%20implement%20any%20additional%20forms%20of%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPew%20Research%20Center%20recently%20conducted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewtrusts.org%2Fen%2Fresearch-and-analysis%2Farticles%2F2024%2F09%2F17%2Fnew-survey-finds-financial-constraints-are-driving-missed-student-loan-payments%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%201%2C533%20borrowers%20that%20highlighted%20the%20impact%20the%20on-ramp%20period%20had%20on%20those%20who%20could%20not%20afford%20their%20monthly%20payments.%20According%20to%20Pew%2C%2013%25%20of%20borrowers%20did%20not%20make%20payments%20during%20the%20on-ramp%2C%20and%2076%25%20of%20those%20borrowers%20cited%20financial%20concerns%20as%20the%20key%20reason%20for%20falling%20behind.%20Another%2012%25%20of%20surveyed%20borrowers%20reported%20inconsistent%20payments%2C%20making%20them%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20delinquency%20once%20the%20on-ramp%20period%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20on-ramp%2C%20a%20separate%20program%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-i-qualify-for-fresh-start-student-loan-debt-forgiveness-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFresh%20Start%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20coming%20to%20an%20end.%20Fresh%20Start%20began%20in%202022%20to%20return%20borrowers%20in%20delinquency%20or%20default%20into%20good%20standing%20before%20entering%20repayment%2C%20and%20the%20Education%20Department%20planned%20to%20end%20that%20program%20on%20October%201.%20However%2C%20BI%20first%20reported%20on%20Monday%20that%20technical%20difficulties%20accessing%20the%20Fresh%20Start%20website%20led%20the%20department%20to%20extend%20the%20deadline%20to%20October%202%20at%203%20a.m.%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20other%20forms%20of%20relief%20remain%20blocked%20in%20court.%20Along%20with%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20Biden's%20broader%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20plan%20under%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-federal-court-debt-cancellation-biden-borrowers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efacing%20a%20temporary%20restraining%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20the%20administration%20cannot%20move%20forward%20with%20implementing%20the%20relief%20pending%20a%20final%20legal%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-on-ramp-period-ending-credit-scores-consequences-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727775362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626c0f9786fa90001905d195%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-on-ramp-period-ending-credit-scores-consequences-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20on-ramp%20period%20for%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20is%20over.%20This%20means%20those%20who%20miss%20payments%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20negative%20credit%20reporting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-on-ramp-period-ending-credit-scores-consequences-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Atishi%20claims%20LG%20directed%20police%20not%20to%20let%20her%20meet%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727775204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113846296%2Cimgsize-82406.cms%22%