4100100626_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20Microsoft%20manager.%20AI%20saves%20me%20time%20on%20some%20tasks%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20work%20any%20less.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naga%20standing%20infront%20of%20mountains%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6c7d575c877a99b61389d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%2037-year-old%20manager%20at%20Microsoft%20says%20AI%20has%20reduced%20the%20time%20he%20spends%20on%20busywork%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20rush%20to%20scale%20AI%20has%20also%20resulted%20in%20more%20deadlines.%3Cp%3ENaga%20Santhosh%20Reddy%20Vootukuri%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%2037-year-old%20manager%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-pay-data-shows-how-much-more-ai-workers-make-2024-8%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20AI%20has%20changed%20his%20workflow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20reduced%20his%20time%20spent%20on%20coding%20by%2070%25%2C%20and%20also%20cut%20time%20spent%20on%20reading%20and%20meetings%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20given%20the%20rush%20to%20scale%20AI%2C%20he%20also%20says%20the%20time%20saved%20is%20spent%20on%20meeting%20quicker%20deadlines%20and%20shipping%20updates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%2037-year-old%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fnaga-santhosh-reddy-vootukuri-5a67a133%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENaga%20Santhosh%20Reddy%20Vootukuri%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20software%20engineer%20manager%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20which%20is%20heavily%20invested%20in%20AI.%20This%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20his%20identity%2C%20employment%2C%20and%20pay%20rates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20launched%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20was%20shocked.%20As%20a%20developer%2C%20I%20loved%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20at%20Microsoft%20for%20close%20to%2014%20years%20and%20I've%20been%20a%20manager%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20Before%20ChatGPT%20came%20out%2C%20I%20would%20say%2080%25%20of%20my%20daily%20work%20was%20spent%20on%20coding%2C%20and%2020%25%20was%20looking%20into%20documentation%2C%20writing%2C%20brainstorming%20with%20my%20team%2C%20and%20helping%20junior%20engineers%20with%20various%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-investing-billions-into-chatgpt-creator-openai-partnership-2023-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMicrosoft%2520is%2520backing%2520up%2520the%2Cbillions%2520into%2520ChatGPT%2520creator%2520OpenAI%26amp%3Btext%3DMicrosoft%2520is%2520making%2520a%2520%2527multi%2Cplanning%2520a%2520%252410%2520billion%2520investment.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWith%20OpenAI%20and%20Microsoft's%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20have%20all%20the%20tools%20we%20need%20directly%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20it's%20tightly%20integrated%20within%20Word%2C%20Outlook%2C%20PowerPoint%2C%20and%20Visual%20Studio%2C%20which%20is%20the%20bread%20and%20butter%20for%20what%20developers%20use%20to%20write%20code%20in%20different%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20AI%20has%20changed%20my%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22671686b8-c732-4333-83e4-84767da9b67a%5C%22%3EIt's%20reduced%20the%20time%20I%20spend%20on%20coding%20by%2070%25%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20developer%2C%20AI%20has%20significantly%20improved%20my%20efficiency%20and%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20manager%2C%20my%20responsibility%20is%20to%20go%20through%20my%20team's%20code%20and%20make%20sure%20it's%20100%25%20quality-efficient%20so%20that%20I%20can%20merge%20it%20into%20main%20production%20before%20we%20release%20and%20deploy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20have%20to%20manually%20look%20at%20each%20and%20every%20line%20change.%20But%20with%20the%20integration%20with%20AI%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-jobs-at-risk-replacement-artificial-intelligence-ai-labor-trends-2023-02%23tech-jobs-coders-computer-programmers-software-engineers-data-analysts-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E70%25%20of%20my%20time%20has%20been%20reduced.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20AI%20tool%20integrates%20my%20past%20history%20of%20comments%20to%20give%20me%20code%20comments%20and%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20also%20saves%20me%20time%20with%20meetings.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20so%20difficult%20for%20me.%20I%20used%20to%20accept%20most%20of%20the%20meetings%2C%20but%20then%20I%20informed%20people%20that%20if%20they're%20not%20targeting%20questions%20directly%20to%20me%2C%20I'm%20not%20able%20to%20attend.%20I%20would%20ask%20them%20to%20record%20the%20meeting%20and%20share%20it%20with%20me%20so%20that%20I%20can%20go%20through%20it%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20AI%2C%20I%20get%20an%20automated%20transcript%20of%20a%20summary%20of%20what%20has%20been%20discussed.%20It%20also%20breaks%20down%20tasks%20or%20action%20items%20I%20have%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20tools%20are%20100%25%20accurate%2C%20but%20I%20would%20say%2095%25%20to%2096%25%20of%20the%20time%20it's%20completely%20accurate%2C%20and%20it's%20constantly%20improving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20also%20saves%20me%20time%20with%20reading.%20If%20a%20group%20is%20releasing%20a%20new%20feature%2C%20I%20need%20to%20go%20through%20each%20design%20document%20and%20give%20as%20much%20feedback%20as%20possible.%20There%20could%20be%2010%20to%2015%20lengthy%20design%20documents%20and%20they%20contain%20all%20the%20nitty-gritty%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Copilot%20integrated%20in%20Word%2C%20a%20ribbon%20appears%20at%20the%20top%20of%20documents%2C%20and%20I%20get%20a%20complete%20summary.%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20spend%20X%20hours%20reading%20the%20entire%20document.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20a%20similar%20tool%20within%20email%20if%20you're%20added%20to%20a%20big%20email%20thread%20and%20don't%20have%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22717592bc-a50c-43d9-a1da-f2dbeaa11fc5%5C%22%3EI%20still%20have%20a%20full%20workload%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20has%20definitely%20helped%20with%20skipping%20mundane%20tasks%2C%20that's%20not%20exactly%20what%20my%20team's%20work%20is%20focused%20on.%20Whatever%20time%20I'm%20getting%20back%20from%20leveraging%20AI%2C%20I'm%20using%20it%20for%20some%20other%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20role%2C%20I%20talk%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20customers%20about%20released%20products%20and%20they%20always%20come%20back%20and%20ask%20for%20more%20features.%20Then%20I%20have%20to%20sit%20with%20my%20team%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20strategy%20for%20release.%20AI%20can't%20be%20used%20in%20these%20situations.%20Once%20the%20developers%20start%20writing%20code%20for%20these%20projects%20and%20do%20the%20actual%20work%2C%20that's%20where%20we%20leverage%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Microsoft%2C%20we%20follow%20a%20management%20framework%20called%20a%20Scrum%20model%2C%20and%20it%20means%20we%20release%20in%20sprints.%20Every%20two%20weeks%2C%20we%20target%20finishing%20some%20work%20items%20and%20we%20try%20to%20finish%20it.%20Earlier%2C%20it%20could%20take%20two%20or%20three%20years%20for%20Microsoft%20to%20deliver%20major%20releases.%20But%20with%20the%20current%20model%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-dump-announcements-feels-never-ending-gartner-analyst-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteams%20are%20releasing%20updates%20monthly%20or%20sometimes%20even%20weekly%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20living%20in%20a%20competitive%20world.%20If%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-new-bing-making-google-show-can-dance-bard-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20is%20releasing%20something%2C%20Microsoft%20has%20to%20counteract%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20with%20some%20other%20cool%20feature.%20So%20that's%20why%20developers%20are%20using%20AI%20wherever%20they%20can%20to%20reduce%20their%20time%2C%20but%20they%20are%20using%20any%20time%20saved%20for%20other%20tasks%20or%20other%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20work%20for%20a%20product-based%20company%20in%20the%20software%20industry%2C%20even%20if%20you%20are%20getting%20time%20back%2C%20you%20cannot%20just%20sit%20and%20relax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-manager-ai-reduces-busywork-not-daily-workload-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727773742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6c7d575c877a99b61389d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-manager-ai-reduces-busywork-not-daily-workload-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20Microsoft%20manager%2C%20AI%20has%20helped%20automate%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20tasks.%20But%20that%20time%20saved%20goes%20back%20into%20releasing%20more%20products%20and%20features.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-manager-ai-reduces-busywork-not-daily-workload-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Siddaramaiah%20brushes%20off%20allegations%20after%20wife%20decides%20to%20return%20MUDA%20plots%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727773595000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113845