0future%20thanks%20to%20their%20competitive%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20main%20component%20is%20valuation.%20Valuations%20need%20to%20be%20reasonable%20enough%20to%20expect%20solid%20returns%20going%20forward.%20Many%20of%20the%20stocks%20in%20the%20fund%2C%20like%20Nvidia%2C%20for%20example%2C%20weren't%20added%20until%20they%20had%20pullbacks%20large%20enough%20to%20make%20them%20compelling%2C%20Umansky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20putting%20a%20stock%20in%20the%20fund%2C%20Umansky%20said%20he%20has%20so%20much%20confidence%20in%20the%20quality%20and%20advantages%20of%20the%20business%20that%20he%20intends%20to%20hold%20it%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20Umansky%20about%20some%20of%20the%20holdings%20he's%20particularly%20excited%20about%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20recent%20additions%2C%20and%20some%20that%20have%20resided%20in%20the%20fund%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261220cb3-3a46-4a1d-b58a-a05562417b81%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E8%20stocks%20Umansky%20is%20betting%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUmansky%2C%20who%20also%20manages%20the%20Baron%20Fifth%20Avenue%20Growth%20Fund%20(BFTHX)%2C%20which%20is%20up%2047%25%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%2C%20said%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20a%20pervading%20theme%20in%20many%20of%20his%20picks%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20research%20suggests%20that%20this%20is%20going%20to%20dramatically%20change%20the%20way%20people%20do%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Umansky%20said%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20pick%20some%20of%20the%20winners%20in%20areas%20like%20software%20and%20services%2C%20there%20are%20clear%20winners%20emerging%20in%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroadcom%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Favgo-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAVGO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20%3Cstrong%3ETaiwan%20Semiconductor%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Ftsmc-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETSMC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20two%20examples%2C%20Umansky%20said.%20The%20semiconductor%20producers%20make%20up%204.1%25%20and%204.3%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20of%20the%20Baron%20Durable%20Advantage%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20the%20plumbing%2C%20basically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20sell%20the%20ammunition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20the%20firms%20have%20very%20strong%20balance%20sheets%20with%20free%20cash%20flow%20yields%20above%205%25.%20Umansky%20said%20the%20two%20stocks%20were%20recent%20additions%20to%20the%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20some%20software-oriented%20firms%20whose%20revenues%20are%20already%20seeing%20a%20boost%20from%20AI%2C%20Umansky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeta%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmeta-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMETA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EMicrosoft%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmsft-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMSFT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EAmazon%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Famzn-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAMZN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20three%20included%20in%20his%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeta%20is%20already%20generating%20billions%20of%20dollars%20from%20artificial%20intelligence%20by%20being%20able%20to%20target%20better%2C%20by%20improving%20engagement%2C%20and%20by%20getting%20better%20click-through%20rates%2C%26quot%