E%3Cp%3EBoth%20machines%20require%20human-like%20perception%20of%20fast-changing%20surroundings%20and%20instantaneous%20reactions%20with%20little%20room%20for%20error.%20They%20also%20both%20require%20immense%20amounts%20of%20what%20Huang%20sells%3A%20AI%20computing%20power.%20But%20robotics%20is%20a%20tiny%20portion%20of%20Nvidia's%20revenue%20today.%20And%20growing%20it%20isn't%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Nvidia's%20place%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-3-trillion-club-apple-microsoft-jensen-huang-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20stratosphere%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20to%20be%20permanent%2C%20Huang%20needs%20the%20market%20for%20robotics%20to%20be%20big.%20Though%20the%20story%20of%20Nvidia's%20last%20few%20years%20has%20been%20one%20of%20incredible%20engineering%2C%20foresight%2C%20and%20timing%2C%20the%20challenge%20to%20make%20robots%20real%20may%20be%20even%20tougher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248af91f2-ff7b-4976-9a95-fea6d922ba9f%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20Nvidia%20bring%20on%20the%20robots%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20presents%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvcs-like-khosla-and-a16z-backing-robotics-that-use-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emassive%20unlock%20for%20robotics.%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20scaling%20the%20field%20means%20making%20the%20engineering%20and%20building%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRobotic%20AI%20is%20the%20most%20complicated%20because%20a%20large%20language%20model%20is%20software%2C%20but%20robots%20are%20a%20mechanical%20engineering%20problem%2C%20a%20software%20problem%2C%20and%20a%20physics%20problem.%20It's%20much%20more%20complicated%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-demand-nvidia-databank-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaul%20Martynek%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CEO%20of%20data%20center%20landlord%20Databank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20people%20working%20on%20robotics%20are%20experts%20with%20doctoral%20degrees%20in%20robotics%20because%20they%20have%20to%20be.%20The%20same%20was%20true%20of%20language-based%20AI%2010%20years%20ago.%20Now%20that%20foundation%20models%20and%20computing%20to%20support%20them%20are%20widely%20available%2C%20it%20doesn't%20take%20a%20doctorate%20to%20build%20AI%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-cuda-software-gpu-ai-chips-cerebras-ipo-2024-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSince%2520CUDA%2520is%2520perhaps%2520the%2CNvidia%2520is%2520worth%2520the%2520fight.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELayers%20of%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20vast%20language%20and%20image%20libraries%20are%20intended%20to%20make%20users%20stickier%20and%20lower%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20so%20that%20almost%20anyone%20can%20build%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20robotics%20stack%20needs%20to%20do%20the%20same%2C%20but%20since%20using%20AI%20in%20physical%20spaces%20is%20harder%2C%20making%20it%20work%20for%20laymen%20is%20also%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nvidia%20robotics%20stack%20takes%20some%20navigating.%20It's%20a%20sea%20of%20platforms%2C%20libraries%2C%20and%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmniverse%20is%20a%20simulation%20platform.%20It%20offers%20a%20virtual%20world%20that%20developers%20can%20customize%20and%20use%20to%20test%20simulations%20of%20robots.%20%26quot%3BIsaac%26quot%3B%20is%20what%20Nvidia%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bgym%26quot%3B%20built%20on%20top%20of%20Omniverse.%20It's%20how%20you%20put%20your%20robot%20into%20an%20environment%20and%20practice%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJetson%20Thor%26quot%3B%20is%20Nvidia's%20chip%20for%20powering%20robots.%20Project%20Groot%2C%20which%20the%20company%20refers%20to%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmoonshot%26quot%3B%20initiative%2C%20is%20a%20foundation%20model%20for%20humanoid%20robots.%20In%20July%2C%20the%20company%20launched%20a%20synthetic%20data%20generation%20service%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnvidianews.nvidia.com%2Fnews%2Fnvidia-accelerates-worldwide-humanoid-robotics-development%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOsmo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20software%20layer%20that%20ties%20it%20all%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20often%20touts%20that%20humanoids%20are%20easier%20to%20build%20because%20the%20world%20is%20already%20made%20for%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20easiest%20robot%20to%20adapt%20in%20the%20world%20are%20humanoid%20robots%20because%20we%20built%20the%20world%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20Computex.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20more%20data%20to%20train%20these%20robots%20because%20we%20have%20the%20same%20physique%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGathering%20data%20about%20how%20we%20move%20still%20takes%20time%2C%20effort%2C%20and%20money.%20Tesla%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20paying%20people%20%2448%20per%20hour%20to%20perform%20tasks%20in%20a%20special%20suit%20to%20train%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-job-training-optimus-robot-motion-capture-suit-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehumanoid%2C%20Optimus%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20been%20the%20biggest%20problem%20in%20robotics%20%E2%80%94%20how%20much%20data%20is%20needed%20to%20give%20those%20foundational%20models%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20world%20and%20adjust%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-this-engineer-hacked-her-career-and-became-a-gm-at-microsoft-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESophia%20Velastegui%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20AI%20expert%20who's%20worked%20for%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20analysts%20see%20the%20potential.%20Research%20firm%20William%20Blair's%20analysts%20recently%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BNvidia's%20capabilities%20in%20robotics%20and%20digital%20twins%20(with%20Omniverse)%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20scale%20into%20massive%20businesses%20themselves.%26quot%3B%20The%20analysts%20expect%20Nvidia's%20automotive%20business%20to%20grow%2020%25%20annually%20through%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20announced%20that%20BMW%20uses%20Isaac%20and%20Omniverse%20to%20train%20factory%20robots.%20Boston%20Dynamics%2C%20BYD%20Electronics%2C%20Figure%2C%20Intrinsic%2C%20Siemens%2C%20and%20Teradyne%20Robotics%20use%20Nvidia's%20stack%20to%20build%20robot%20arms%2C%20humanoids%2C%20and%20other%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20three%20robotics%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20so%20far%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20failed%20to%20lower%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20for%20want-to-be%20robot%20builders%20as%20it%20has%20in%20language%20and%20image-based%20AI.%20Competitors%20are%20coming%20in%20to%20try%20to%20open%20up%20the%20ideal%20stack%20for%20robotics%20before%20Nvidia%20can%20dominate%20that%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20developing%20AI%20that%20can%20interact%20with%20the%20physical%20world%20is%20extremely%20challenging.%20That's%20why%20we%20developed%20an%20entire%20platform%20to%20help%20companies%20train%20and%20deploy%20robots%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Nvidia%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20via%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20company%20launched%20a%20humanoid%20robot%20developer%20program.%20After%20submitting%20a%20successful%20application%20developers%20can%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eaccess%20all%20of%20these%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254d5849a-4e51-475e-b8c8-bccca9f22c1e%5C%22%3ENvidia%20can't%20do%20it%20alone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAshish%20Kapoor%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20all%20the%20progress%20the%20field%20has%20yet%20to%20make.%20For%2017%20years%20he%20was%20a%20leader%20in%20Microsoft's%20robotics%20research%20department.%20There%2C%20he%20helped%20to%20develop%20Airsim%2C%20a%20computer%20vision%20simulation%20platform%20launched%20in%202017%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-shutters-project-airsim-ai-strategy-openai-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esunsetted%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKapoor%20left%20with%20the%20shutdown%20to%20make%20his%20own%20platform.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20founded%20Scaled%20Foundations%20and%20launched%20Grid%2C%20a%20robotic%20development%20platform%20designed%20for%20aspiring%20robot%20builders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20company%20can%20solve%20the%20tough%20problems%20of%20robotics%20alone%2C%20Kapoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20I've%20seen%20it%20happen%20in%20AI%2C%20the%20actual%20solution%20came%20from%20the%20community%20when%20they%20worked%20on%20something%20together.%20That's%20when%20the%20magic%20started%20to%20happen%2C%20and%20this%20needs%20to%20happen%20in%20robotics%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20feels%20like%20every%20player%20aiming%20for%20humanoid%20robots%20is%20in%20it%20for%20themselves%2C%20Kapoor%20said.%20But%2C%20there's%20a%20robotics%20startup%20graveyard%20for%20a%20reason.%20The%20robots%20get%20into%20real-world%20scenarios%20and%20they%20are%20simply%20not%20good%20enough.%20Customers%20give%20up%20on%20them%20before%20they%20can%20get%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20running%20joke%20is%20that%20every%20robot%20has%20a%20team%20of%2010%20people%20trying%20to%20run%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrid%20offers%20a%20free%20tier%20or%20a%20managed%20service%20that%20offers%20more%20help.%20Scaled%20Foundations%20is%20building%20its%20own%20foundation%20model%20for%20robotics%2C%20but%20also%20encourages%20users%20to%20develop%20one%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20elements%20of%20Nvidia's%20robotics%20stack%20are%20open%20source.%20And%20Huang%20often%20touts%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20working%20with%20every%20robotics%20and%20AI%20company%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20but%20some%20developers%20fear%20the%20juggernaut%20will%20protect%20its%20own%20success%20first%2C%20and%20support%20the%20ecosystem%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20doing%20the%20Apple%20effect.%20To%20me%2C%20they're%20trying%20to%20lock%20you%20in%20as%20much%20as%20they%20can%20into%20their%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jonathan%20Stephens%2C%20chief%20developer%20advocate%20at%20computer%20vision%20firm%20EveryPoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Nvidia%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20this%20perception%20is%20inaccurate.%20The%20company%20%26quot%3Bcollaborates%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20leading%20players%20in%20the%20robotics%20and%20humanoid%20developer%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20them%20deploy%20robots%20faster.%20%26quot%3BOur%20success%20comes%20from%20the%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaled%20Foundations%20and%20Nvidia%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20working%20on%20a%20foundation%20model%20for%20robotics.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvcs-like-khosla-and-a16z-backing-robotics-that-use-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESkild%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Eraised%20%24300%20million%20in%20July%20to%20build%20its%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22973ca613-a524-4878-942d-bb11cf703d83%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20a%20humanoid%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESimulators%20are%20an%20essential%20stop%20on%20the%20path%20to%20humanoid%20robots%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20necessarily%20lead%20to%20human-like%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20describing%20a%20robotic%20arm%20at%20Computex%2C%20Huang%20said%20that%20Nvidia%20supplies%20%26quot%3Bthe%20computer%2C%20the%20acceleration%20layers%2C%20and%20the%20pre-trained%20AI%20models%26quot%3B%20needed%20to%20put%20an%20AI%20robot%20into%20an%20AI%20factory.%20The%20goal%20of%20using%20robotic%20arms%20in%20factories%20at%20scale%20has%20been%20around%20for%20decades.%20Robotic%20arms%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspectrum.ieee.org%2Funimation-robot%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20cars%20since%201961%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20Huang%20was%20talking%20about%20an%20AI%20robot%20%E2%80%94%20an%20%3Cem%3Eintelligent%3C%2Fem%3E%20robot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arms%20that%20build%20cars%20are%20largely%20unintelligent.%20They%20are%20programmed%20to%20perform%20repetitive%20tasks%20and%20often%20%26quot%3Bsee%26quot%3B%20with%20sensors%20instead%20of%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AI-enabled%20robotic%20arm%20would%20be%20able%20to%20handle%20varied%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20picking%20up%20diverse%20items%20and%20putting%20them%20down%20in%20diverse%20places%20without%20breaking%20them%2C%20maybe%20while%20on%20the%20move.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20perceive%20objects%20and%20guardrails%20and%20then%20make%20moves%20in%20a%20coherent%20order.%20But%20a%20humanoid%20robot%20is%20a%20world%20away%20from%20even%20the%20most%20useful%20non-humanoid.%20Some%20roboticists%20doubt%20that%20it's%20the%20right%20target%20to%20aim%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20skeptical.%20The%20cost%20to%20make%20a%20humanoid%20robot%20and%20to%20make%20it%20versatile%20is%20going%20to%20be%20higher%20than%20if%20you%20make%20a%20robot%20that%20doesn't%20look%20like%20a%20human%20and%20can%20only%20do%20a%20single%20task%20but%20does%20the%20task%20well%20and%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20former%20Nvidia%20robotics%20expert%20with%20more%20than%2015%20years%20in%20the%20field%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Huang%20is%20all%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Jensen%20has%20an%20obsession%20with%20robots%20because%2C%20ultimately%2C%20what%20he's%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20create%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Martynek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaming%20and%20graphics%20aren't%20Nvidia's%20future%20anymore.%20Autonomous%20cars%20and%20robotics%20are.%20The%20company%20told%20BI%20it%20expects%20everything%20to%20be%20autonomous%20in%20the%20future%20starting%20with%20robotic%20arms%20and%20vehicles%20and%20leading%20to%20buildings%20and%20even%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20at%20Apple%20when%20we%20developed%20iPad%20inspired%20by%20Star%20Trek%20and%20other%20future%20worlds%20in%20movies%2C%26quot%3B%20Velastegui%20said.%20Robotics%20tap%20into%20our%20imagination%2C%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-robots-huamanoid-self-driving-cars-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727773202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6b9dfde59ade1a3b533d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-robots-huamanoid-self-driving-cars-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jensen%20Huang's%20vision%20for%20Nvidia%20includes%20advancing%20AI-driven%20robotics%2C%20but%20technical%20and%20market%20hurdles%20could%20impact%20the%20company's%20ambitious%20goals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%20(Emma%20Cosgrove)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-robots-huamanoid-self-driving-cars-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%E2%80%99s%209Network%20Hitches%20Itself%20to%20%E2%80%98Married%20at%20First%20Sight%E2%80%99%20Hit%20Reality%20Show%20%E2%80%93%20Global%20Bulletin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727773152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fmarried-at-first-sight1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236161304%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MARRIED%20TO%20HIT%20REALITY%20SHOW%20Australia%E2%80%99s%209Network%20has%20acquired%20every%20season%20of%20every%20English-language%20version%20of%20hit%20reality%20show%20%E2%80%9CMarried%20at%20First%20Sight.%E