%20time%3B%20excited%20and%20equally%20emotional.%20That%20was%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20family%20of%20Thomas%20Cheriyan%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kerala%2C%20whose%20body%20had%20been%20recovered%2056%20years%20after%20an%20ill-fated%20aircraft%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20crashed%20over%20the%20Rohtang%20Pass%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheriyan's%20body%20was%20among%20the%20four%20recovered%20through%20a%20search%20mission%2C%20the%20Army%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20twin-engine%20turboprop%20transport%20aircraft%20AN-12%2C%20carrying%20102%20people%2C%20had%20gone%20missing%20on%20February%207%2C%201968%2C%20while%20flying%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20Leh.%20For%20decades%2C%20the%20wreckage%20and%20remains%20of%20the%20victims%20remained%20lost%20in%20the%20icy%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheriyan%20was%20from%20Elanthoor%20in%20Pathanamthitta%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20explain%20the%20situation.%20We%20are%20equally%20happy%20and%20sad%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20siblings%20of%20Cheriyan%20told%20reporters%20at%20their%20ancestral%20home%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20siblings%20said%20they%20never%20expected%20that%20they%20would%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20a%20formal%20adieu%20to%20their%20beloved%20brother%20decades%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%2012%20when%20the%20aircraft%20crash%20happened.%20I%20still%20have%20vivid%20memories%20of%20my%20brother.%20He%20used%20to%20bring%20us%20so%20many%20things%20whenever%20he%20came%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Cheriyan's%20sister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fatal%20accident%20happened%20when%20Cheriyan%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20his%20posting%20after%20completing%20his%20training%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalled%20that%20he%20had%20come%20home%20two%20or%20three%20times%20after%20joining%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20is%20feeling%20relieved%20now%20as%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20all%20the%20last%20rites%20for%20him%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20consider%20the%20recovery%20of%20his%20mortal%20remains%20as%20a%20great%20blessing.%20We%20thank%20God%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20would%20be%20buried%20in%20their%20local%20parish%20after%20performing%20all%20the%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20younger%20brothers%20also%20expressed%20heartfelt%20happiness%20and%20gratitude%20to%20the%20Army%20and%20the%20nation%20for%20showing%20this%20much%20consideration%20and%20respect%20to%20the%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%2C%20however%2C%20shared%20their%20dismay%20at%20not%20having%20any%20photo%20of%20their%20deceased%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20hoped%20that%20the%20Army%20could%20help%20to%20get%20them%20one%20from%20their%20old%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmy%20officials%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20bodies%20were%20found%20by%20a%20joint%20team%20comprising%20personnel%20from%20the%20Dogra%20Scouts%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20Tiranga%20Mountain%20Rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20in%202003%20when%20mountaineers%20from%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Institute%20of%20Mountaineering%20discovered%20the%20wreckage%2C%20sparking%20multiple%20expeditions%20over%20the%20years%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20especially%20the%20Dogra%20Scouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dogra%20Scouts%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20search%20missions%20in%202005%2C%202006%2C%202013%2C%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20five%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20recovered%20by%202019%20in%20view%20of%20the%20treacherous%20conditions%20and%20unforgiving%20terrain%20of%20the%20crash%20site%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandra%20Bhaga%20Mountain%20Expedition%20has%20now%20recovered%20four%20more%20bodies%2C%20bringing%20renewed%20ho