hies%20and%20athletes%20alike%2C%20is%20launching%20a%20new%20smart%20ring%20this%20month%3A%20Bloomberg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oura%20ring%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6137d2bceedea900193d76b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOura%20is%20debuting%20a%20fourth-generation%20smart%20ring%20this%20October%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3Cp%3EMegan%20Hernbroth%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOura%20Health%20Oy%20is%20releasing%20a%20new%20smart%20ring%20this%20month%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Tom%20Hale%20said%20that%20the%20company%20expects%20to%20double%20its%20annual%20sales%20this%20year%2C%20to%20around%20%24500%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20faces%20increasing%20competition%20from%20products%20like%20Samsung's%20latest%20Galaxy%20Ring.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOura%20Health%20Oy%20is%20set%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20rings%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-09-30%2Foura-nears-500-million-in-annual-revenue-and-readies-new-ring%3Fsrnd%3Dphx-latest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Finnish%20company's%20fourth%20generation%20of%20fitness-tracking%20rings%20will%20feature%20a%20slimmer%20design%2C%20improved%20battery%20life%2C%20and%20more%20accurate%20activity%20tracking.%20Sources%20told%20Bloomberg%20that%20this%20marks%20the%20company's%20most%20significant%20product%20update%20in%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOura%20has%20sold%20more%20than%202.5%20million%20rings%20since%20its%20founding%2011%20years%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesswire.com%2Fnews%2Fhome%2F20240614157633%2Fen%2F%25C5%258CURA-Helping-Millions-of-People-Improve-Their-Health-S