ch%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20appeared%20for%20three%20states%20--%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Asked%20if%20being%20accused%20in%20a%20criminal%20case%20can%20be%20a%20ground%20for%20facing%20bulldozer%20action%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20absolutely%20not%2C%20even%20for%20heinous%20crimes%20like%20rape%20or%20terrorism.%20Like%20my%20lord%20said%20it%20cannot%20also%20be%20that%20the%20notice%20issued%20is%20stuck%20one%20day%20before%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20there%20are%20different%20laws%20for%20municipal%20corporations%20and%20panchayats.%20%26quot%3BThere%20should%20also%20be%20an%20online%20portal%20so%20people%20are%20aware%2C%20once%20you%20digitise%20it%20there%20is%20a%20record.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20then%20said%20he%20was%20worried%20that%20the%20court%20was%20issuing%20directions%20based%20on%20a%20few%20instances%20alleging%20that%20one%20community%20was%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20secular%20country%20and%20our%20directions%20will%20be%20for%20all%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religion%20or%20community.%20Of%20course%2C%20for%20encroachment%2C%20we%20have%20said...%20if%20it%20is%20on%20a%20public%20road%2C%20footpath%2C%20water%20body%20or%20railway%20line%20area...%20If%20there%20is%20any%20religious%20structure%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%2C%20be%20it%20gurudwara%20or%20dargah%20or%20temple%2C%20it%20cannot%20obstruct%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20unauthorised%20construction%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20one%20law%2C%20it%20is%20not%20dependent%20on%20religion%20or%20faith%20or%20beliefs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Vrinda%20Grover%20appears%20for%20UN%20Rapporteur%20and%20makes%20arguments%20on%20housing%20availability.%20The%20Soli