ry%20commanders%20on%20both%20sides%20to%20take%20those%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClashes%20between%20India%20and%20China%20began%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20marking%20a%20turning%20point%20and%20deteriorating%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20Despite%2021%20rounds%20of%20Corps%20Commander-level%20talks%2C%20critical%20friction%20points%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20such%20as%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%2C%20remain%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727764200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-06%2F8d20anpg_ladakh-genericpixabay_650x400_17_June_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fties-not-normal-with-china-want-pre-2020-situation-on-ground-army-chief-6690101%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20situation%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20with%20China%20is%20%26quot%3Bstable%20but%20not%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Indian%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi.%20General%20Dwivedi%20said%20the%20current%20state%20of%20affairs%20remains%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fties-not-normal-with-china-want-pre-2020-situation-on-ground-army-chief-6690101%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Janhvi%20revealed%20that%20Khushi%20bullied%20her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727764165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113840039%2Cimgsize-40154.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-janhvi-kapoor-revealed-that-khushi-kapoor-bullied-her-during-childhood-gave-proof-with-an-adorable-video%2Farticleshow%2F113840058.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimes