ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fe14oe91_jammu-and-kashmir-elections_625x300_01_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20final%20phase%20of%20voting%20for%20the%2090-member%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20assembly%20is%20today.%20This%20phase%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20as%2024%20of%20these%20seats%20are%20located%20in%20Hindu-dominated%20Jammu.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20test%20for%20Engineer%20Rashid's%20party%20in%20North%20Kashmir%2C%20where%2016%20seats%20will%20determine%20whether%20its%20performance%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20was%20a%20fluke.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20assembly%20election%20in%20the%20state%20since%202014.%20While%20Phase%201%20recorded%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2061.38%25%2C%20the%20second%20phase%20saw%20relatively%20lower%20voting%20of%2056.79%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E10%20Candidates%20Per%20Seat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20from%20major%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20have%20addressed%20rallies%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%20A%20total%20of%20415%20candidates%20are%20contesting%20for%2040%20seats%2C%20averaging%20roughly%2010.4%20candidates%20per%20seat-the%20highest%20among%20all%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%2016%20seats%20are%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20districts%20of%20Baramulla%2C%20Bandipora%2C%20and%20Kupwara.%20As%20many%20as%20202%20candidates%20are%20contesting%20here%2C%20averaging%2012.6%20candidates%20per%20seat.%20Among%20them%2C%2069%20are%20independents%20and%2049%20from%20smaller%20parties%2C%20together%20making%20up%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20candidate%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2025%2C%20Baramulla%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20candidates%2C%20while%20Gurez%2C%20an%20ST-reserved%20seat%2C%20has%20just%20five%20names%20in%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%2C%2024%20seats%20are%20up%20for%20grabs.%20These%20lie%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Jammu%2C%20Udhampur%2C%20Samba%2C%20and%20Kathua.%20As%20many%20as%20213%20candidates%20are%20vying%20for%20these%20assembly%20segments%20-%20an%20average%20of%208.9%20candidates%20per%20seat.%20Sixty-nine%20candidates%20are%20fighting%20independently%20while%2065%20are%20from%20smaller%20parties%3B%20together%20they%20make%20up%2060%25%20of%20the%20total%20contestants%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2017%2C%20Jammu%20North%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20candidates%2C%20while%20Akhnoor%2C%20an%20SC-reserved%20seat%2C%20has%20the%20lowest%2C%20just%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Candidate%20Pool%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20pool%20includes%2018%20names%20from%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%2C%2025%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%2029%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%2033%20from%20the%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%2017%20from%20the%20Apni%20Party%20(JKAP%2C%20a%20splinter%20group%20of%20PDP%20founded%20by%20Altaf%20Bukhari)%2C%2014%20from%20the%20People's%20Conference%20(JKPC)%2C%2016%20from%20Engineer%20Rashid's%20Awami%20Ittehad%20Party%20(AIP)%2C%20and%2011%20from%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad's%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Azad%20Party%20(DPAP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20NC%20are%20in%20friendly%20competition%20in%20three%20seats%3A%20Baramulla%2C%20Sopore%2C%20and%20Nagrota.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20are%20138%20independents%20and%20114%20candidates%20from%20smaller%20parties%2C%20which%20together%20comprise%2060%25%20of%20the%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20delimitation%20process%2C%20three%20seats%20no%20longer%20exist%3A%20Sangrama%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20and%20Raipur%20Domana%20and%20Gandhi%20Nagar%20in%20Jammu.%20Seven%20new%20seats%20have%20been%20created%3A%20Jasrota%2C%20Ramgarh%2C%20Jammu%20North%2C%20Udhampur%20West%2C%20and%20Bahu%20in%20Jammu%2C%20along%20with%20Trehgam%20and%20Wagoora%20Kreeri%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20net%20basis%2C%20four%20seats%20have%20been%20added%20-%20three%20in%20Jammu%20and%20one%20in%20North%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%202014%20Results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20out%20of%2036%20seats%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20won%20five%2C%20the%20PDP%20seven%2C%20the%20BJP%2018%2C%20the%20Congress%20two%2C%20and%20the%20Others%20four.%20A%20close%20contest%20was%20observed%20in%2015%20seats%2C%20with%20victory%20margins%20of%2010%25%20or%20less.%20Notably%2C%20the%20second%20runner-up%20received%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20victory%20margin%20in%2019%20seats%2C%20complicating%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20Congress%20recorded%2018%25%20votes%2C%20the%20PDP%2016%25%2C%20the%20NC%2017%25%2C%20the%20BJP%2029%25%2C%20and%20Others%2020%25.%20Had%20NC%20and%20the%20Congress%20contested%20as%20an%20alliance%20in%202014%2C%20they%20could%20have%20won%2017%20of%20the%2036%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Kashmir%20used%20to%20be%20a%20traditional%20stronghold%20of%20the%20NC%2C%20but%20the%20region's%20loyalty%20shifted%20to%20the%20PDP%20after%20its%20emergence.%20The%20PDP%20won%2010%20and%20seven%20seats%20out%20of%2015%20in%202002%20and%202014%2C%20respectively.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20the%20NC%20that%20won%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20Engineer%20Rashid%20caused%20an%20upset%20by%20defeating%20NC%20chairman%20Omar%20Abdullah%20in%20the%20Baramulla%20seat%20by%202%2C04%2C000%20votes.%20His%20party%2C%20the%20AIP%2C%20was%20leading%20in%2014%20segments%2C%20while%20Sajjad%20Lone's%20People's%20Conference%20was%20leading%20in%20one%20of%20the%2018%20assembly%20segments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmaller%20Parties%20And%20Independents%20Can%20Queer%20The%20Pitch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20People's%20Conference%20garnered%201%2C73%2C000%20votes%2C%20the%20PDP%20received%2027%2C000%2C%20and%2013%20independents%20collectively%20bagged%2070%2C000%20votes.%20This%20illustrates%20how%20independents%20and%20smaller%20parties%20could%20not%20only%20harm%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%20but%20also%20win%20a%20few%20seats%20from%20the%20valley.%20The%20Apni%20Party%20and%20Engineer%20Rashid's%20AIP%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20legacy%20parties.%20Many%20former%20separatists%20are%20contesting%20as%20independents%2C%20potentially%20acting%20as%20vote-splitters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%20allege%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20behind%20the%20rise%20of%20these%20new%20parties%20and%20candidates%2C%20claiming%20they%20are%20acting%20as%20proxies%20for%20it.%20The%20Valley%20also%20has%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20independents%20and%20smaller%20parties%20compared%20to%20Jammu%2C%20where%20the%20contest%20is%20largely%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Kashmir's%20Baramulla%20and%20Kupwara%20districts%20have%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20Pahari-speaking%20communities%2C%20comprising%2014%25%20and%2012%25%20of%20their%20populations%2C%20respectively.%20The%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20gain%20ground%20by%20fulfilling%20their%20long-pending%20demand%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20ST%20list.%20The%20party's%20logic%20is%20that%20these%20communities%20are%20likely%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%2C%20which%20did%20not%20meet%20their%20demands%2C%20and%20instead%20support%20'Others'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%2C%20Congress%20Strategies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20strategy%20aims%20to%20secure%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20seats%20from%20Jammu%20in%20Phase%203%2C%20hoping%20that%20seats%20in%20North%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20split%20among%20legacy%20and%20new%20parties%2C%20thereby%20weakening%20the%20NC-Congress%20front's%20chances%20of%20forming%20a%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20is%20optimistic%20that%20its%20revival%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20and%20an%20improved%20strike%20rate%20in%20direct%20contests%20against%20the%20BJP%20will%20help%20it%20reduce%20the%20latter's%20tally%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhmad%20Guru%20To%20Muzaffar%20Beig%2C%20Key%20Names%20In%20The%20Fray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20candidates%20include%20Ahmad%20Guru%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20Afzal%20Guru%20hanged%20in%202013%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%202001%C2%A0%20Parliament%20attack.%20He%20is%20contesting%20from%20Sopore%20as%20an%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople's%20Conference%20Chief%20Sajjad%20Lone%20is%20contesting%20from%20two%20seats%2C%20Kupwara%20and%20Handwara%2C%20and%20Engineer%20Rashid's%20brother%20Kursheed%20Ahmad%20is%20contesting%20from%20Langate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20former%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%2C%20Tara%20Chand%20(Congress)%20and%20Muzaffar%20Beig%20(Independent)%20are%20contesting%20from%20Chhamb%20and%20Baramulla%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20phase%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20elections%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20leading%20political%20parties%2C%20with%20constituencies%20of%20many%20prominent%20candidates%20at%20stake.%20A%20fierce%20contest%20is%20on%20the%20cards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727763720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fe14oe91_jammu-and-kashmir-elections_625x300_01_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%