EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Zakir%20Naik's%20team%20announced%2C%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Pakistan%20Dr%20Zakir%20Naik%20%26amp%3B%20Shaikh%20Fariq%20Naik's%20Pakistan%20Tour%202024%20Public%20Talks%3A%20Karachi%20-%205th%20%26amp%3B%206th%20Oct%20Lahore%20-%2012th%20%26amp%3B%2013th%20Oct%20Islamabad%20-%2019th%20%26amp%3B%2020th%20Oct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20August%2020%2C%20while%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20Malaysian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwar%20Ibrahim%20said%20that%20if%20sufficient%20evidence%20is%20presented%20in%20the%20case%20related%20to%20fugitive%20preacher%20Zakir%20Naik%20then%20the%20country%20will%20'not%20condone%20terrorism'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%2050th%20Sapru%20House%20Lecture%20the%20Malaysian%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20talking%20about%20sentiment%20of%20extremism%2C%20of%20compelling%20case%2C%20evidence%20that%20suggest%20that%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20an%20individual%2C%20group%20or%20factions%20or%20parties.%20These%20are%20of%20concern%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZakir%20Naik%20is%20known%20for%20his%20inflammatory%20speeches%20and%20is%20currently%20wanted%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20under%20a%202016%20money%20laundering%20case.%20He%20is%20also%20alleged%20to%20have%20incited%20people%20by%20his%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaik%20runs%20a%20channel%20by%20the%20name%20PeaceTV%2C%20which%20is%20banned%20across%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20due%20to%20its%20controversial%20nature%20and%20he%20has%20also%20been%20denied%20entry%20into%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727762640000%2C%22visual