Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20are%20the%20heroes%20behind%20the%20rescues%20chosen%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMen%20and%20women%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2030%20years%20who%20know%20swimming%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20saving%20victims%20are%20eligible%20to%20become%20Drishti%20lifesavers%2C%20notes%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COur%20hiring%20checklist%20includes%20thorough%20physical%20tests%2C%20interviews%2C%20reference%20checks%2C%20and%20police%20verification.%20The%20physically%20demanding%20nature%20of%20a%20lifesaver%20requires%20that%20men%20and%20women%20who%20apply%20should%20possess%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20physical%20fitness%20and%20our%20training%20team%20does%20the%20rest.%20Every%20lifesaver%20must%20be%20capable%20of%20swimming%20400%20metres%20in%20under%2011%20minutes.%20They%20need%20to%20quickly%20assess%20the%20capabilities%20and%20risks%20of%20individuals%20involved%20in%20aquatic%20activities%2C%20follow%20on-site%20protocols%2C%20and%20provide%20emergency%20medical%20services%20when%20required%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20goes%20on%20to%20claim%2C%20%E2%80%9CDrishti%E2%80%99s%20450-strong%20lifesaver%20team%20undergoes%20a%20rigorous%20annual%20refresher%20course%20to%20maintain%20and%20improve%20their%20emergency%20response%20skills%2C%20physical%20fitness%2C%20and%20communication%20abilities.%20The%20training%20includes%20CPR%2C%20first%20aid%2C%20beach%20operations%2C%20jet%20ski%20use%2C%20rescue%20equipment%20handling%2C%20and%20various%20rescue%20techniques.%20In%20addition%20to%20lifesaving%20skills%2C%20they%20also%20receive%20training%20in%20leadership%20and%20soft%20skills%20to%20effectively%20manage%20public%20interactions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-em