0glass%20floor%20towards%20the%20entrance.%20Another%20treasure%20lay%20in%20uncovering%20the%20historic%20gantry%20that%20once%20facilitated%20the%20transport%20of%20ice%20slabs.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20room%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98giant%20ice%20tray%E2%80%99%20where%20ice%20was%20manufactured.%20There%20were%20four-foot-deep%20pits%20with%20refrigerant%20coils%20running%20alongside%20that%20would%20freeze%20the%20water%20in%20the%20pits.%20The%20massive%20ice%20blocks%20were%20then%20picked%20up%20using%20a%20crane%20and%20moved%20to%20an%20area%20where%20they%20would%20be%20cut%20and%20distributed%20for%20their%20final%20purpose.%E2%80%9D%20During%20restoration%2C%20the%20raised%20floor%20was%20wood%20panelled%20and%20can%20be%20opened%20to%20reveal%20the%20pits.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20architect%E2%80%99s%20lens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20almost%20as%20if%20time%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20ticked%20within%20the%20Ballard%20Estate%20neighbourhood%20of%20South%20Mumbai.%20With%20its%20neoclassical%20architecture%2C%20defunct%20railway%20station%2C%20which%20once%20saw%20a%20host%20of%20British%20passengers%20board%20steamers%2C%20and%20remnants%20of%20the%20colonial%20era%2C%20the%20South%20Bombay%20pincode%20is%20almost%20a%20bubble%20frozen%20in%20time.%20Copious%20amounts%20of%20ice%20were%20manufactured%20every%20day%2C%20which%20made%20their%20way%20from%20the%20factory%20to%20the%20restaurants%2C%20fish%20markets%20and%20vegetable%20markets%20across%20South%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20beguiling%20history%20of%20the%20ice%20factory%20that%20drew%20Malik%20to%20this%20project.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20also%20the%20intention%20to%20convert%20this%20place%20into%20a%20meeting%20spot%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365250%2Fvinyasa-earth-sankalp-sharma-sustainable-homestay-jaipur-artist-resid